    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in good condition. It runs and drives well with no significant mechanical issues. The exterior has minor wear consistent with normal use, including a few small scratches, but no major dents or damage. The interior is clean and well-maintained with only light signs of use.",
